{"tid":1548243,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做個負責任既香港人 咪再以訛傳訛！","createTime":"2019-09-07T03:15:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T03:15:03.000Z","uid":260709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2ba8b98fe7835cabf6e87f6702d416d41b3dd175","tid":1548243,"uid":260709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:15:03.000Z","msg":"謠言、猜想、朋友既朋友既message、未肯定既消息，唔該明顯地，顯著地，毫不含糊地，註明只系<span style=\"color: red;\">傳聞</span>，唔好當系一般新聞甘傳開去。一般人唔會逐件事細思慢想，所以唔該幫幫手。<br />\n<br />\n雖然好多時消息fact check唔到，但如果廣泛流傳既信息，到最後被踢爆唔系事實既全部，對運動既傷害可以好大。所以請講明系傳聞。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPS 法新社話你聽fact check 是咁做的<br />\n<a href=\"https://factcheck.afp.com/fact-checking-how-we-work\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffactcheck.afp.com%2Ffact-checking-how-we-work&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAS1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=a05390ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://factcheck.afp.com/fact-checking-how-we-work</a>"}]}